node.text: Thank you @rootspicnic @theroots @questlove @michelleobama and Thank you @traceeellisross for that beautiful introduction. ❤️ I had so much fun doing this. And thank you to the band 🙏🏽 Black artists and black music has shaped the DNA of my artistic being since I was a little girl. I am so honored and will never ever take for granted the love and respect I have been blessed to receive from the black community as an Iranian woman making Soul and R&B music. ❤️ Peace, Love n Light.
